<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/103000805/2025-26/evaluation> a ns1:EvaluationSystem ;
    ns1:evaluationDescription """Progressive evaluation and global evaluation:

The grade of all practice exams will consider the attendance and participation. The minimum grade required for the practice exercises is 3/10 and the minimum grade for passing the course is 5/10 in the final grade.

Referred evaluation:

All practice exercises can be submitted again to pass the course in the referred evaluation."""@es ;
